      <p>Scenes let you control multiple devices at the same time with a single tap or a custom schedule.</p>
      <hr />
      <div class="example">
        <h4>I'm Home</h4>
        <p>Turn on the lights and unlock the front door when you arrive home.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="example">
        <h4>Away</h4>
