      </div>
      <div class="example">
        <h4>Wake Up</h4>
        <p>Turn on the lights at 30% brightness and turn off the night lights when you wake up to automate your morning routine.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="example">
        <h4>Good Night</h4>
        <p>Arm the alarm, lock the doors, and turn off the lights when you turn in for the night.</p>
      </div>
